    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (v2 / ((v0 + 0.05 * v2 + 0.15) + (v2 + 0.11 + v2 + 0.97)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(0.21) / wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.98)))
    v2 = 0.87
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.22)) - wp.cos(tmp))
    v2 = 0.49
    data[tid] = v0
